    FOR CUSTOMER NAME
_________________________________________________________
[A-Z] match a single capital letter (first letter of name)

[a-z]* match any number of small letters (other letters or name)

(\s) match 1 whitespace character (the space between names)

+ one or more of the previous expression (to match more than one name)

all together:

- matches first names / lastname -
^([A-Z][a-z]*((\s)))+[A-Z][a-z]*$

example
Omkar Kulkarni
Omkar Sunil Kulkarni

----------------------------------------------------------------------

FOR CUSTOMER EMAIL

So some of the email addresses that will be valid via this email validation technique are:
   user@domain.com
   user@domain.co.in
   user1@domain.com
   user.name@domain.com
   user#@domain.co.in
   user@domaincom

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

